{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Herding cats is easy! Said no one\u2026ever</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your main job in Catizens is to build your town around the personality traits of its inhabitants. Just like in real life, cats require personal attention and special treatment. Combinations of different personality traits and moods affect their proficiency and obedience. Catizens form relationships with each other and will occasionally issue personal requests, so you will need to learn what makes each cat happy in order to stay on their good side. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/957660/extras/2_Upgrade.png?t=1736859793\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Create unique cats and design the perfect home</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick from an assortment of facial and body features, as well as personality traits to create cats with distinct looks and temperaments. Design a place just for them by decorating your settlements with pieces of furniture, plants and other items. The better furnished a town is, the happier your catizens will be. So get creative! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/957660/extras/5_Perfect_home.png?t=1736859793\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build and manage your settlement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Catizens can learn a variety of professions \u2013 from farming, to blacksmithing or offering protection from local wildlife. Different building types unlock depending on the traits and professions available. There\u2019s no need to micromanage the entire settlement when it gets large. Invest your time and attention in a few outstanding cats and let them become town leaders.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/957660/extras/3_Build.png?t=1736859793\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore the wilderness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Develop your settlement, complete objectives and expand to areas with different environments that offer new adventures. Carefully examine your surroundings to find the best fishing spots, hidden treasures and quirky characters that may offer a quest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/957660/extras/4_Challenges.png?t=1736859793\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"I'm a Lumberjack, Pa!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/957660/360546f8b93409c63d3b88a5986b470806bfa660.jpg"},{"name":"Here Fishy Fishy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/957660/9f653b0aba2e38fb41221583b685625b541dd2ee.jpg"},{"name":"Long Live the King!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/957660/72f617682925f654a24de199113bc720fd85b88c.jpg"},{"name":"Simple Pleasures","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/957660/b7f5ec45b77f2813db211270b8fe432466e1531b.jpg"},{"name":"Off to Work We Go","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/957660/ca3760e08c8273ec2cd14ad4e7ff7f0ffe8660b5.jpg"},{"name":"Mmm ... Pork Chops","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/957660/1225648eff896f0d18ebc65dc48d115af1b0bf94.jpg"},{"name":"New Friends!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/957660/75efec3068732d3c87e12a9af346c3e7bcd8f557.jpg"},{"name":"Sad to See You Go","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/957660/aab497ed8fe731cc42f5a95f6a715acdb76ded30.jpg"},{"name":"Fire and Brimstone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.